comments.content:
Meta-pathways of proteins involved in three MAPPS of beta-oxidation.

This MAPP is only present for statistical purpose, to help evaluate all beta-oxidation MAPPS at once. Omit the 3 individual sub-mapps from statistical evaluation to prevent redundancy.
